# === How it works ===
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "How it works"

msgid "This plugin analyzes email headers (Message-ID, References, Thread-Index) to automatically combine related emails into the same ticket, preventing duplicates when CC recipients use \"Reply to All\"."
msgstr "This plugin analyses email headers (Message-ID, References, Thread-Index) to automatically combine related emails into the same ticket, preventing duplicates when CC recipients use \"Reply to All\"."

